description: Located on the thriving West Side of South Boston, near the Seaport, this 2 bedroom 2 bathroom home offers exceptional living space and amenities. The convenience of deeded garage parking for two, close proximity to West Broadway, Financial District, Seaport District, Logan Airport and the Broadway T make this a very convenient place to live in the City. Enjoy a spacious open living room with gas fireplace, an open kitchen with granite topped counters, stainless steel appliances and working island that seats four. Well cared for condo association with several updates since construction in 2004. This condo is in pristine overall condition and ready for you to call it home.
